Terren Peizer Results








Terren Peizer








Terren  Peizer








American investment manager

Terren  Peizer

Terren S. Peizer, chronicled by the LA Times as a financial prodigy,and often called the "Zelig of Wall Street" is currently the Chairman of a Los Angeles-based investment company, Socius Capital Group. Since its inception in June 2009 to December 2011, SCG has provided companies with capital commitments and funding in excess of $500 million.








